nodes.text: Kliskud was a Glottalphib female piratess who operated during the last decades of the Galactic Republic. After the J'feh crime lord Skijid Vrescot acquired the space station the Wheel for the purposes of distributing Tirefin spice, Vrescot made a deal with Kliskud whereby he allowed her a free reign to strike against shipping in the vicinity of the Wheel in return for her help in combating his rival spice dealers. However, Vrescot reneged on the agreement after Kliskud's activities began to dissuade gamblers from visiting the Wheel, and the piratess responded by consuming the J'feh.
